== External Links ==
* [https://www.kunaicho.go.jp/ryobo/guide/026/index.html Mishima Aino Mausoleum] - Imperial Household Agency
* [https://www.city.sakai.lg.jp/kanko/rekishi/dkofun/Ranking/zenkoku.html Rankings of Kofun areas (Sakai City)]

